Albert LANE, Appellant, v. C. S. METROPOLITAN MARKET COMPANY, a Corporation, Appellee. No. 11202. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 18, 1947. Frisbie & Hoogs and William H. Iloogs, all of Berkeley, Cal., for appellant. Hanna & Morton, B. W. Burkhead, and John H. Blake, all of Los Angeles, Cal.; for appellee.

Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS, and ORR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURT AM.

The judgment of the District Court, 62 F.Supp. 89, is affirmed.
